Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:38.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,百萬  美元  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\rENG}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:51.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能打敗他！你能打敗他！\N{\rENG}You got him! You got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只遇見過一個我不想和他爭鬥的人\N{\rENG}I only ever met one man I wouldn't wanna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:11.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我止不了血\N{\rENG}I can't stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,滾開吧，你個沒有的東西\N{\rENG}Get out of here, you useless tit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我遇見他的時候 他已經是拳擊界最好的傷口護理師\N{\rENG}When I met him, he was already the best cut man in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能止住嗎？\N{\rENG}Can you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,從60年代起就開始做訓練師和經理人 一直保持著高昂的熱情\N{\rENG}Started training and managing in the '60s, but he never lost his gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:32.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我來看看他\N{\rENG}Let me have a look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,他沒事，他沒事\N{\rENG}He's fine. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你止不了血的話就不是沒事\N{\rENG}He ain't if you don't stop this bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:38.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,我再給你一個回合\N{\rENG}I'll give you one more round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 時間到了，來吧    - 我們怎麼辦？告訴我怎麼辦\N{\rENG}- Seconds out. Let's go.    - What do we do? Tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你讓他打你\N{\rENG}You let him hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,有時你就是無能為力\N{\rENG}Sometimes there's just nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,傷口太深, 離骨頭太近\N{\rENG}Cut's too wide, too close to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許是斷了一條血管...\N{\rENG}Maybe you got a severed vein...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,...或者你就是無法讓止血藥深入裡面\N{\rENG}...or you just can't get the coagulant deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 加油！    - 分開，分開\N{\rENG}- Come on!    - Break. Break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:06.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,在肌肉的不同層次\N{\rENG}There are all kinds of combinations you come up against...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,你會遇到各種不同的問題組合\N{\rENG}...down in the different layers of meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,而弗蘭基全都知道如何解決\N{\rENG}...and Frankie knew how to work every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 對！加油！    - 你在做什麼？\N{\rENG}- That's it! Come on!    - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,打倒他，威利！\N{\rENG}Knock him out, Willie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,人們熱愛暴力\N{\rENG}People love violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們會在車禍現場 減慢車速查看死屍\N{\rENG}They'll slow down at a car wreck to check for bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是這些人宣稱他們熱愛拳擊\N{\rENG}Same people claim to love boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們根本不瞭解拳擊是什麼\N{\rENG}They got no idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,拳擊是有關尊嚴\N{\rENG}Boxing is about respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,贏得你自己的...\N{\rENG}Getting it for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,...同時剝奪對手的\N{\rENG}...and taking it away from the other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,我先去發動車\N{\rENG}I'll warm up the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,鄧先生？\N{\rENG}Mr.Dunn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我欠你錢？\N{\rENG}I owe you money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有，先生\N{\rENG}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我認識你媽媽？\N{\rENG}I know your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,這個我確實不知道，先生\N{\rENG}Don't rightly know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 那你想幹什麼？    - 我參加了墊場賽\N{\rENG}- Then what is it you want?    - I was on the undercard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,而且我也贏了 我是麥琪 菲斯傑拉德\N{\rENG}I won my fight too. Maggie Fitzgerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼，麥琪 菲斯傑拉德，有什麼事嗎？\N{\rENG}Well, Maggie Fitzgerald, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你有沒有正好看了我的比賽？    - 沒有\N{\rENG}- Did you happen to see it?    - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我幹的不錯\N{\rENG}I did pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你也許有興趣訓練我\N{\rENG}Thought you might be interested in training me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不訓練女孩子\N{\rENG}I don't train girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:31.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許你應該試試 看我打過的人都說我很兇狠\N{\rENG}Maybe you should. People see me fight say I'm pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,小姐, 光是兇狠並不夠\N{\rENG}Girlie, tough ain't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是個錯誤\N{\rENG}It's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,車應該能向後退的，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}Car should be able to back up, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,幫我推一下，行不？\N{\rENG}Just push, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 霍根有什麼事？    - 邀請我們參加頭銜戰\N{\rENG}- What did Hogan want?    - Offered us a title shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,是時候了\N{\rENG}About time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,我直接把他拒絕了\N{\rENG}I turned him down flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,再多打兩三場比賽 你就準備充分了\N{\rENG}Two or three more fights, you'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,好久以前就說是兩三場比賽了，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}Been two or three more fights for a long time now, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽著，威利 你只有一次機會贏得冠軍\N{\rENG}Look, Willie, you get one shot at the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,輸掉的話 可能就再沒有機會了\N{\rENG}You lose it, it may not come around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,再多打兩三場比賽 我們就準備充分了\N{\rENG}Now, two or three more fights and we'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,都聽你的，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}Whatever you say, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基總喜歡說 拳擊是一種不自然的運動\N{\rENG}Frankie liked to say that boxing is an unnatural act...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為拳擊中的每樣東西都是逆向的\N{\rENG}...that everything in boxing is backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,有時...\N{\rENG}Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,...打出一記重拳 的最好方法是退後一步\N{\rENG}...best way to deliver a punch is step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的主啊，請盡力...\N{\rENG}Well, do your best, Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,...保護凱蒂\N{\rENG}...protect Katy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有安妮\N{\rENG}Annie too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,至於其他的...\N{\rENG}Other than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:09.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,...你知道我想要什麼 所以我再重復也沒有什麼用\N{\rENG}...you know what I want, there's no use me repeating myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:14.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是退後太多 你就已經退出比賽了\N{\rENG}But step back too far, you ain't fighting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,（聖馬可教堂）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 再見    - 再見\N{\rENG}- Bye.    - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,神父，佈道很精彩，讓我流淚\N{\rENG}Father, that was a great sermon. Made me weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這周又有什麼疑惑？\N{\rENG}What's confusing you this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,噢，就是那個老掉牙的三位一體的問題\N{\rENG}Oh, it's the same old one-God-three-God thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基, 大多數人幼兒園的時候 就知道一切都是信心的問題\N{\rENG}Frankie, most people figure out by kindergarten it's about faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:49.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,是不是有點象三種不一樣的薩其馬 都裝在一個大盒子裡？\N{\rENG}Is it sort of like Snap, Crackle and Pop all rolled up in one big box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:53.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,你站在我的教堂外面 把上帝比做點心？\N{\rENG}You're standing outside my church comparing God to Rice Krispies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,你來做彌撒的唯一原因 就是要騷擾我\N{\rENG}The only reason you come to Mass is to wind me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不過今天不會了    - 我有點迷惑\N{\rENG}- It won't happen this morning.    - I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不，你沒有    - 不，我有\N{\rENG}- No, you aren't.    - Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,那好，我給你的答案是： 只有一位上帝\N{\rENG}Then here's your answer: There's one God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有事嗎？我很忙\N{\rENG}Anything else? Because I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 那麼聖靈呢？    - 他是上帝的愛的一種表現形式\N{\rENG}- What about the Holy Ghost?    - He's an expression of God's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 耶穌呢？    - 上帝之子，別在這兒裝傻了\N{\rENG}- And Jesus?    - Son of God. Don't play stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼他是什麼呢？ 上帝的兒子意味著半神半人？\N{\rENG}What is he then? Does that make him a demigod?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有半神半人 操他媽的異教徒！\N{\rENG}There are no demigods, you fucking pagan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 給你女兒寫信了麼？    - 當然\N{\rENG}- Did you write your daughter?    - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這是對一個神父撒謊\N{\rENG}Now you're lying to a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟你說吧，休息一天 明天別來了\N{\rENG}You know what? Take a day off, don't come to Mass tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,（鬥場拳擊館）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,有些人會說對於一個拳手來說 最重要的莫過於熱情\N{\rENG}Some people would say the most important thing a fighter can have is heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基則會說 “給我一個只有熱情的拳手...\N{\rENG}Frankie would say, "Show me a fighter who's nothing but heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,...我會告訴他什麼叫鼻青臉腫”\N{\rENG}...and I'll show you a man waiting for a beating."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:03.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我只見過一個全心投入的拳手\N{\rENG}Think I only ever met one fighter who was all heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:08.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的名號是“戰鬥小子” 丹吉爾 迪拉德 巴奇...\N{\rENG}My name's Dangerous Dillard Fighting Flippo Bam-Bam Barch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,...來自德克薩斯布勞德縣！\N{\rENG}...out of Broward County, T exas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,丹吉爾是幾年前來的\N{\rENG}Danger showed up a couple of years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,他和他媽媽的新男友艾瑞威爾 一起到洛杉磯來\N{\rENG}He'd come visiting L.A. With Ervel, his mama's new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:27.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,似乎艾瑞威爾迷了路 自己回去了德克薩斯\N{\rENG}Apparently Ervel got lost and ended up back in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:32.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,在來這裡以前 丹吉爾找了他大概一個星期\N{\rENG}Danger looked for him for about a week before he introduced himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:38.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，你知道麼 我對黑鬼從來沒有任何偏見\N{\rENG}Hey, you know, I gots nothing against niggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,呃，真高興聽你這麼說\N{\rENG}Well, that's nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯，我的家鄉很多人確實是那樣...\N{\rENG}Yeah, lots of people where I comes from does...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:50.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,...但是我媽媽告訴我 不要傷害任何人...\N{\rENG}...but my mama taught me not to cause hurt to no man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,...不管是不是黑鬼\N{\rENG}...niggers or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你媽媽還真是個好人 我可以幫你點什麼嘛？\N{\rENG}You got a nice mama. Anything else I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也許只是隨便問個問題  ...\N{\rENG}Just one of those questions you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,...但是丹吉爾總想給你最好的答案\N{\rENG}...but Danger wanted to give it his best answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:04.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想成為次中量級世界冠軍\N{\rENG}Well, sir, I'd likes to become the welterweight champion of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要挑戰“城市機動眼鏡蛇”...\N{\rENG}And I challenge the Motor City Cobra...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,...還有“刺客”湯馬斯 赫爾斯...\N{\rENG}...Thomas "Hit Man" Hearns...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:15.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,...爭奪次中量級世界冠軍！\N{\rENG}...to fight me for the welterweight championship of the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,冒失鬼，閉嘴 你連排名都沒有\N{\rENG}Yo, Flip, shut up, man! You ain't even ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,你最少要打一場比賽才能有排名\N{\rENG}You gotta have at least one fight to be ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:24.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，我可以和任何人打，隨時！\N{\rENG}Hey, I'll fight any man, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，你是個壞蛋，是嗎？\N{\rENG}Hey, you a bad man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,進繩圈裡來，我陪你玩一回合\N{\rENG}Get in the ring. Go a round with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 謝瑞爾    - 沒問題\N{\rENG}- Shawrelle.    - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,別理他\N{\rENG}Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,丹吉爾, 你繼續訓練\N{\rENG}Danger, you go on back to training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:40.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會的，斯科雷普先生\N{\rENG}Will do, Mr.Scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的緊身褲不錯\N{\rENG}Them's some nice tights, Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我以後再揍你的屁股 小妞\N{\rENG}I'll give you that ass-whupping later, Olive Oyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:51.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的褲子還真不賴，丹吉爾\N{\rENG}Hey, bro, those pants look real pretty on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,把他媽媽的緊身衣還給她吧\N{\rENG}Give his mama back her tights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:57.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝瑞爾 貝裡的左鉤拳 可以打飛一輛坦克 ...\N{\rENG}Shawrelle Berry had a left hook that would move a tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:09:00.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,...但是他的心胸卻象豆子一樣小\N{\rENG}...but he had a heart the size of a split pea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基17年前從巴比 馬龍 手裡買下了鬥場拳擊館\N{\rENG}Frankie bought the Hit Pit from Bobby Malone 17 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:08.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,巴比想搬到佛羅裡達去 而弗蘭基想要生活有點保障\N{\rENG}Bobby wanted to move to Florida, and Frankie wanted some security.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:11.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,巴比在他收拾行李的時候死掉了\N{\rENG}Bobby died while he was packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基那時候才發現 大多數拳擊館都虧錢\N{\rENG}And Frankie found out most gyms lose money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:18.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我已經告訴過你 別讓丹吉爾繼續訓練下去了\N{\rENG}I thought I told you I didn't want Danger working out here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:20.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,他又不會傷害到別人，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}He ain't hurting nothing, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,他傷害到我了\N{\rENG}Well, he's hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:27.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看著心疼 看他朝著空氣揮拳，好象空氣會反擊一樣\N{\rENG}Breaking my heart, watching him punch the air like he thinks it's gonna punch back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有我告訴你多少次了 漂白液就是漂白液\N{\rENG}And how many times have I gotta tell you that bleach is bleach?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就不能買便宜點的麼？ 不用買貴的那種\N{\rENG}Why can't you buy the cheap stuff? You don't have to buy the expensive stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,這種更好聞一些，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}It smells better, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:39.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,漂白液聞起來還是漂白液\N{\rENG}Bleach smells like bleach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 嘿，斯科雷普    - 嘿，威利先生\N{\rENG}- Hey, Scrap.    - Hey, Mr.Willie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，昨晚打得不錯\N{\rENG}Hey, nice fight last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,打得不錯\N{\rENG}Nice fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 大個子威利    - 嘿，賽利\N{\rENG}- Big Willie.    - Hey, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 打得不錯    - 謝了，兄弟\N{\rENG}- Nice fight.    - Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人在談話\N{\rENG}People are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,這他媽的是什麼語言？\N{\rENG}What the hell kind of language is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想幹嗎？\N{\rENG}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你可能想知道 你有一個拳手...\N{\rENG}I thought you might like to know you got a fighter out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,...不跟別的經理人說話\N{\rENG}...not talking to another manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,不跟別的經理人說話？\N{\rENG}Not talking to another manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是隨便什麼經理人\N{\rENG}And not just any manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,米奇 麥克\N{\rENG}Mickey Mack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:53.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你進來就是為了跟我說大個子威利 不跟米奇 麥克說話\N{\rENG}You came in here to tell me that Big Willie is not talking to Mickey Mack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:56.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們兩個人，一個字都沒說\N{\rENG}Not a word. Neither one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我正打算讀書\N{\rENG}I'm trying to read here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧，如果你覺得讀書更重要\N{\rENG}Well, if you think that's more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,新來的那個女孩是誰？\N{\rENG}Who's your new girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼？\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的老天\N{\rENG}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,最好快點\N{\rENG}Better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,她要繼續這麼打沙袋 手腕遲早會斷\N{\rENG}She keeps hitting it like that, she gonna break her wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在浪費時間 我告訴過你我不訓練女人\N{\rENG}You're wasting your time. I told you I don't train girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你也許會改變主意\N{\rENG}Thought you might change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,外面有至少一打訓練師訓練女人 找到一個很容易\N{\rENG}Dozens of trainers train girls. You won't have any trouble finding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不需要一打，老闆 您一個就會很好\N{\rENG}Don't hardly need a dozen, boss. You'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:48.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,別叫我老闆，我不是你老闆 你別再這麼叫了\N{\rENG}Don't call me boss, now. I'm not your boss, and don't you be calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 威利，你準備好了麼？    - 隨時可以開始\N{\rENG}- Willie, you ready to work?    - Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果我不叫你老闆 你會訓練我麼？\N{\rENG}If I stop calling you boss, will you train me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,那我還是繼續這樣叫您好了\N{\rENG}Then I might as well keep calling you it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,她從密蘇裡州西南部來...\N{\rENG}She came from southwestern Missouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:08.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,...歐紮克地區的小城鎮 西奧多西亞城外的山上...\N{\rENG}...the hills outside the scratch-ass Ozark town of Theodosia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:13.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,...一個雪松和橡樹環繞 比偏僻更偏僻的地方\N{\rENG}...set in the cedars and oak trees somewhere between nowhere and goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:17.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,在成長的過程中她只知道一件事： 自己是個垃圾\N{\rENG}She grew up knowing one thing: She was trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,是給我的狗的\N{\rENG}It's for my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:38.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,盡管她可以跋涉1800英里 西奧多西亞還是就在那山上\N{\rENG}She'd come 1800 miles, but Theodosia was still just over the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在打沙袋，老闆\N{\rENG}Working the bag, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:03.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不是你的老闆 還有，是沙袋在打你\N{\rENG}I'm not your boss. And that bag's working you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,把錢退給她\N{\rENG}Give her her money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你確定？\N{\rENG}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 她付了多少錢？    - 六個月的\N{\rENG}- How much did she pay?    - Six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我的老天    - 我去還給她\N{\rENG}- Jesus Christ.    - No, I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，別裝聰明瞭，好嗎？\N{\rENG}No, don't be a smartass now, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,這女人一定會覺得咱們為了趕她走...\N{\rENG}Woman thinks I'll throw away six months' worth of dues...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,...連六個月的費用都不要 她肯定會發瘋的\N{\rENG}...just to get rid of her, she's out of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 但是千萬別鼓勵她，明白了麼？    - 好\N{\rENG}- But just don't encourage her, understand?    - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,丹吉爾在外面做什麼？ 他在看什麼？\N{\rENG}And what's Danger doing out there? What's he looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,好象是一瓶水\N{\rENG}Looks like a bottle of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,他付費了麼？\N{\rENG}He paid his dues?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:56.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,費用？ 他連褲子都買不起，你想讓他付訓練費？\N{\rENG}Dues? Boy can't afford pants. Want him to pay dues?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,出去吧\N{\rENG}Get out of my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我操\N{\rENG}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不能把它當做沙袋\N{\rENG}Can't think of it as a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我雖然不是訓練師 但是如果你願意的話我可以示範一下\N{\rENG}I'm not a trainer, but I can show you this if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,任何幫助我都會感激您\N{\rENG}Appreciate any help I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要做的是 你要把它看成是一個人，明白嗎？\N{\rENG}What you wanna do is, you wanna think of it as a man, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在不停地移動\N{\rENG}And he's constantly moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:19.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,沖著你，繞著你 遠離你，明白嗎？\N{\rENG}He's moving towards you, around you, away from you. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:24.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,不要在他向你移動的時候擊打他 因為他會把你向後推...\N{\rENG}Don't hit him when he's coming towards you because he's just gonna push you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,...化解你的擊打 讓你失去平衡，對嗎？\N{\rENG}...he's gonna smother your punches and take your balance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以你要小心的注視他\N{\rENG}So you watch him real carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,不停轉動 這樣你的頭就一直在動\N{\rENG}Keep rotating. That keeps your head moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個肩膀放在後側 這樣你隨時可以打出一記重拳\N{\rENG}And keep one shoulder back so you're always ready to fire a power shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:41.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,對嗎？來，好，好 不停旋轉，不停移動，好\N{\rENG}Right? Go ahead, now. Good, good. Keep rotating, keep moving. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,好，下巴收住\N{\rENG}Good, good. Keep that chin tucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,繼續 不停移動，不停移動\N{\rENG}Come on around. Keep moving, keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 好，好，好    - 象這樣？\N{\rENG}- Good, good, good.    - Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,對，給它幾下\N{\rENG}Yeah. Give it a few shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,下巴收住 下巴收住\N{\rENG}Tuck that chin in, now. Tuck that chin in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常好，很好\N{\rENG}Yeah, that's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,等練完這個 我們就安排你打梨球\N{\rENG}Now, you get this down, we'll put you on the speed bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你有梨球吧\N{\rENG}You do have a speed bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有錢買自己的之前先借用一下\N{\rENG}I'll just borrow it till I can buy my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,好，那你回家吧\N{\rENG}All right, you go on home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我和你一起出去？    - 不用，這裡就是我家\N{\rENG}- I'll walk out with you?    - No, I am home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 想看看嗎？    - 嗯\N{\rENG}- Wanna see?    - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\rENG}It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我再打一會兒會不會打擾您？\N{\rENG}Would it bother you if I worked a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會，走的時候把門關好就行了\N{\rENG}No, just pull the door closed when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果拳擊運動中有訣竅的話...\N{\rENG}If there's magic in boxing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,...那麼這種訣竅就是不停戰鬥 超越耐力的極限...\N{\rENG}...it's the magic of fighting battles beyond endurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:21.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,...超越折斷的肋骨 破裂的腎臟，和脫落的視網膜\N{\rENG}...beyond cracked ribs, ruptured kidneys and detached retinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:37.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,這種訣竅是 為了別人無法瞭解的夢想而賭上一切\N{\rENG}It's the magic of risking everything for a dream that nobody sees but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了，好了，夥計們 看好腳步\N{\rENG}Okay, okay, fellas, watch the footwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，對了，對了\N{\rENG}Hey, that's it. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,手舉起來\N{\rENG}Hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,刺，刺，刺\N{\rENG}Jab, jab, jab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，冒失鬼\N{\rENG}Hey, Flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，冒失鬼，過來\N{\rENG}Hey, Flippy, come here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我找到一個你能打敗的人\N{\rENG}I think I found somebody you can beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不和女人打\N{\rENG}I don't fights women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,為什麼不，兄弟？太合適你了 你知道為什麼嗎？\N{\rENG}Why not, bro? It's perfect, bro, because you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為她--就象你 你可以和他打...\N{\rENG}Because she... Like, you, you could fight to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,...然後可以親親他\N{\rENG}...and then you could kiss to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後你還可以再跟他打一次\N{\rENG}Then you fight to him one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽起來真美啊，哥們兒 象一首詩\N{\rENG}That's beautiful, man. That's like poetry.
