Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.70,1:35:53.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不應該把手放下去的\N{\rENG}I shouldn't have dropped my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.58,1:35:59.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不該轉身的\N{\rENG}I shouldn't have turned.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.72,1:36:08.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,隨時保護我自己\N{\rENG}Always protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.75,1:36:11.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,這句話他和我說了多少遍了\N{\rENG}How many times he tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.06,1:36:14.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊...\N{\rENG}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.53,1:36:17.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,...他說話總是喜歡一遍遍重復\N{\rENG}...he does like to repeat himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.50,1:36:24.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能告訴他我很抱歉嗎？\N{\rENG}Will you tell him I'm real sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.87,1:36:30.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.04,1:36:33.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，我不會這麼做的，麥琪\N{\rENG}I won't do no such thing, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.46,1:36:55.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,真是該死啊\N{\rENG}Damnedest thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.87,1:37:00.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你有什麼計劃？\N{\rENG}So, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.51,1:37:04.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道你已經計劃好了 你還是告訴我的好\N{\rENG}I know you got one, so you might as well tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.98,1:37:06.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,是你的錯\N{\rENG}It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.35,1:37:10.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,對，她現在那樣躺著 都是你的錯\N{\rENG}Yeah, it's your fault she's lying in there like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.51,1:37:12.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,你纏著我讓我訓練她\N{\rENG}You kept after me until I trained her.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.95,1:37:15.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道我不該這麼做的 她再怎麼說也是個女孩\N{\rENG}I knew I shouldn't have done it, her being a girl and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.92,1:37:19.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,其他的一切也不斷向我顯示 不要訓練她\N{\rENG}Everything kept telling me not to.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.56,1:37:21.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,除了你\N{\rENG}Everything but you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.77,1:37:33.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要把你從這兒弄出去\N{\rENG}I'm gonna get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.60,1:37:35.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡的醫生屁都不懂\N{\rENG}These doctors around here don't know squat.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.74,1:37:38.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,要不然他們為什麼要在沙漠裡住著？\N{\rENG}Otherwise, why would they be living out here in the desert?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.58,1:37:41.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,一旦你能被移動了...\N{\rENG}As soon as you're able to be moved...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.15,1:37:45.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,...我會找個地方 有人真正學過醫的地方\N{\rENG}...we'll find some place where they've actually studied medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.69,1:37:50.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你就在那裡修養好了，我會....\N{\rENG}You just rest there, I'II...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.42,1:37:54.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我正在辦\N{\rENG}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.10,1:38:05.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基肯定打遍了全美國醫院的電話...\N{\rENG}Frankie must have called every hospital in America...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.67,1:38:08.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,...尋找能告訴他 她可以被治好的人\N{\rENG}...Iooking for somebody who'd tell him they could fix her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.64,1:38:12.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,有兩次很接近成功 可他們給她做了徹底檢查後...\N{\rENG}He came close twice, till they checked her over...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.04,1:38:15.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,...也表示無能為力\N{\rENG}...said there was nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.55,1:38:18.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩個月後 她病情穩定到可以被移動了\N{\rENG}Took two months till she was stable enough to move.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.02,1:38:26.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們有護士專門做這個，你知道的\N{\rENG}They got nurses for that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.99,1:38:30.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯，可她們太業餘了\N{\rENG}Yeah, but they're amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.37,1:38:46.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為不能移動，她長了褥瘡\N{\rENG}She developed skin ulcers because she couldn't change positions.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.76,1:38:59.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.30,1:39:12.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們坐著救護車 完成了六個小時的旅程\N{\rENG}They made the six-hour trip by ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.05,1:39:26.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,飛過去，開車回來\N{\rENG}Fly there, drive back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.26,1:39:36.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基找到的康復中心 是個不錯的地方\N{\rENG}The rehab center Frankie found was a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.19,1:39:38.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們把麥琪照顧地很周到\N{\rENG}They took good care of Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.16,1:39:41.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,即使他們沒有的話 她也不會抱怨什麼\N{\rENG}She wouldn 't have complained if they hadn 't.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.53,1:39:46.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,每天要花幾小時才能讓她上輪椅\N{\rENG}Took several hours every day to get her ready for the wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.71,1:39:54.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,一，二，三，起\N{\rENG}One, two, three, up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.41,1:39:58.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,由於她無法自主呼吸\N{\rENG}Since she couldn't breathe on her own...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.92,1:40:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,呼吸器總是開著\N{\rENG}...her respirators were always on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.79,1:40:06.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,氧氣24小時不間斷地 被輸進她的身體裡\N{\rENG}Oxygen was pumped into her 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.78,1:40:36.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥琪的媽媽打電話來說 他們會來看她\N{\rENG}Maggie's mama called to say they were all coming for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.35,1:40:39.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,在接下來的兩周裡 她每天都在窗前等他們\N{\rENG}She waited by the window every day for the next two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.96,1:40:42.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\rENG}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.43,1:40:45.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基最後終於追蹤到了他們\N{\rENG}Frankie finally tracked them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.20,1:40:49.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,發現他們六天前就住進旅館了\N{\rENG}Learned they'd checked into their hotel six days earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.37,1:40:52.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基一直給他們留言 但總沒有回音\N{\rENG}Kept leaving messages which were never returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.81,1:40:59.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不用整天都待在這兒\N{\rENG}You don't have to hang around all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.31,1:41:06.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這裡，沒關系的\N{\rENG}I like it here. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.05,1:41:11.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實就算你不在，我也會來讀書的\N{\rENG}In fact, if you weren't here, I'd come here anyway to read my books.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.89,1:41:16.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽媽馬上會來分擔一些負擔的\N{\rENG}Mama will be here soon to share some of the burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.23,1:41:19.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,哦，這不是什麼負擔\N{\rENG}Well, it's no burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.96,1:41:21.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,給\N{\rENG}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.43,1:41:24.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,讀讀這個\N{\rENG}Read this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.88,1:41:35.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了，好了，行了\N{\rENG}Okay, okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.45,1:41:37.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,讀得太糟糕了\N{\rENG}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.38,1:41:43.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我給你翻成英文吧\N{\rENG}Anyway, I'll tell you in English what you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.32,1:41:47.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,上面說：\N{\rENG}It says:
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.96,1:41:51.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,“我要起身去了，去往那茵湖島”\N{\rENG}I will arise and go now And go to Innisfree
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.70,1:41:56.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,“用泥土和樹枝，蓋上一間小木房”\N{\rENG}And a small cabin build there Of clay and wattles made
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.13,1:42:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,“我享受著彼方的寧靜，它緩緩滴零”\N{\rENG}And I shall have some peace there For peace comes dropping slow
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.14,1:42:06.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,“從晨曦的面紗，到蟋蟀歌唱的地方”\N{\rENG}Dropping from the veils of the morning To where the cricket sings.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.21,1:42:10.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,還不賴，對吧？\N{\rENG}Not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.09,1:42:17.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要蓋一間小木屋麼，老闆？\N{\rENG}You gonna build a cabin, boss?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.96,1:42:19.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我？    - 對\N{\rENG}- Me?    - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.16,1:42:24.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道，等你收山之後\N{\rENG}You know, when you quit all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.86,1:42:28.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是說拳擊？\N{\rENG}You mean boxing?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.07,1:42:31.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，我永遠不會收山的\N{\rENG}No, I'll never quit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.70,1:42:35.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我太喜歡那汗臭味道了，我想\N{\rENG}I like the stink too much, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.08,1:42:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想？我看你邊看書...\N{\rENG}You think? Because I could see you there real easy...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.78,1:42:46.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,...邊吃檸檬派很愜意呀\N{\rENG}...with your books and lemon pie.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.32,1:42:51.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,你呢？想在小木屋裡生活麼？\N{\rENG}How about you? Would you like to go live in a cabin?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.26,1:42:55.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我可以學怎麼烤東西\N{\rENG}I could learn how to bake.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.46,1:43:00.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,那樣的話，我....\N{\rENG}Well, then, I'II...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.17,1:43:03.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也許要開始找了\N{\rENG}Maybe I'll start looking then.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.06,1:43:26.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.33,1:43:31.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 去吧    - 好的，聽起來不錯\N{\rENG}- Go ahead.    - All right. Okay, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.63,1:43:38.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，我是弗蘭基 鄧 我們在密蘇裡見過\N{\rENG}Hi, I'm Frankie Dunn. I met you back out in Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.20,1:43:39.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我女兒在哪？\N{\rENG}Where's my little girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.67,1:43:42.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們不應該回旅館換身衣服再來嗎？\N{\rENG}Don't you think you ought to go back to the hotel and change?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.67,1:43:45.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,她還不知道你們已經來了一周 忙著拜訪米老鼠呢\N{\rENG}She doesn't know you've been here a week visiting Woody and Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.61,1:43:49.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們和我妹妹有正事談 你幹嗎不乾脆告訴我們她在哪呢？\N{\rENG}We got business with my sister. Why don't you just tell us where she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.25,1:43:52.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,你肯定是JD 那你肯定是那個談正經事的傢伙？\N{\rENG}Oh, you must be J.D. And you must be the business guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.18,1:43:53.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們錯過了一些東西\N{\rENG}There's some rides you missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.75,1:43:56.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們不如回去 我來告訴她你們來不成了\N{\rENG}Why don't you go back. I'll tell her you couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.59,1:43:58.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我開了這麼遠的路來照顧孩子\N{\rENG}I drove all the way here to take care of my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.02,1:44:01.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,你卻暗示我不是個好母親？\N{\rENG}And you're suggesting I'm not a good mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.36,1:44:03.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥琪哪裡都去不了\N{\rENG}Mary M. Can't go nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.19,1:44:06.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,否則我們早帶她去逛迪士尼樂園了\N{\rENG}If we could've taken her to Disneyland, we would've.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.70,1:44:08.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥琪 菲斯傑拉德?\N{\rENG}Margaret Fitzgerald?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.37,1:44:11.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,就在這裡，301房間\N{\rENG}Right down here, 301.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.37,1:44:13.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 快來，媽媽    - 我們走\N{\rENG}- Come on, Mama.    - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.58,1:44:21.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,後來我看到自己呼吸\N{\rENG}And I saw myself breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.85,1:44:23.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的身體上下起伏\N{\rENG}Like, my body was going up and down.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.88,1:44:26.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想，“為什麼沒人告訴我？”\N{\rENG}I thought, "Why didn't somebody tell me?"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.19,1:44:33.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的頭發得洗了 有點太油了\N{\rENG}Your hair needs washing. It's kind of greasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.14,1:44:48.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,只是些....\N{\rENG}It's just a...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.51,1:44:51.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,只是些法律上的程式\N{\rENG}It's just some kind of legal thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.81,1:44:53.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,是什麼？\N{\rENG}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.28,1:44:55.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們談得怎樣了？\N{\rENG}How we all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.51,1:44:58.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,不好意思，親愛的 我們時間不多\N{\rENG}Sorry, darling, but we ain't got a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.22,1:45:02.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰遜先生收了我們一大筆錢 來保證這件事不出紕漏\N{\rENG}Mr.Johnson's charging us a lot of money to be here to make sure this is done proper.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.55,1:45:05.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們不如把那個留下 我等會兒讀給她聽\N{\rENG}Why don't you just leave that. I'll read it to her later.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.36,1:45:06.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿，老傢伙\N{\rENG}Hey, old man...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.09,1:45:08.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是我們家人麼？\N{\rENG}...you part of our family?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.49,1:45:11.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,別管閑事\N{\rENG}Stay the hell out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.76,1:45:14.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,念給我聽，媽媽\N{\rENG}Read it to me, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.67,1:45:18.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,只是些法律程式 用來保護你的錢的\N{\rENG}Well, it's just something legal to protect your money.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.00,1:45:20.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽媽你不用擔心\N{\rENG}Mama, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.37,1:45:24.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,拳擊協會會支付這裡所有的費用的\N{\rENG}The boxing commission's paying for all this, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.18,1:45:27.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果不呢，麥琪？\N{\rENG}But what if they don't, Mary M?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.48,1:45:30.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,約翰遜先生說他們可以收走我的房子\N{\rENG}Mr.Johnson says they can take my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.48,1:45:33.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你把財產轉移給你母親 那就沒人能動得了了\N{\rENG}If you assign your assets to your mother, no one can touch them.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.82,1:45:35.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,不用管醫生，喪葬費什麼的\N{\rENG}No doctors, no funeral expenses.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.45,1:45:39.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 什麼都不用理會了    - 你看，不如你們把這個留下\N{\rENG}- Nothing.    - Yeah, look, why don't you just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.62,1:45:43.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我以後再讀給她--    - 無意冒犯，這不關你的事\N{\rENG}- Then I'll just read it to her later on...    - With respect, this ain't your business.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.00,1:45:47.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧，我在走廊裡等\N{\rENG}All right. I'll be out in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.64,1:45:56.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一直是個好女兒，麥琪\N{\rENG}You been a good daughter, Mary M.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.61,1:45:59.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你簽了這份文件\N{\rENG}You sign that paper...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.78,1:46:01.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,就能照顧你一家\N{\rENG}...it'll take care of your family...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.18,1:46:04.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,正如你父親所願\N{\rENG}...the way your daddy would've wanted you to.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.19,1:46:11.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗯，你怎麼簽字呢？\N{\rENG}How do you make your mark?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.72,1:46:14.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,能拿住筆麼？\N{\rENG}Can you hold a pen?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.09,1:46:17.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,她只能用牙齒，媽媽\N{\rENG}She gotta do it with her teeth, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.63,1:46:19.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得把筆放到她嘴裡去\N{\rENG}You gotta put it in her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.10,1:46:22.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了，親愛的\N{\rENG}Here you go, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.94,1:46:28.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看了那場比賽麼，媽媽？\N{\rENG}Did you see the fight, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.27,1:46:30.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的 你知道我對那東西是什麼感覺\N{\rENG}Honey, you know how I feel about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.94,1:46:33.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我打得不錯\N{\rENG}I did pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.74,1:46:35.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你輸了，麥琪\N{\rENG}You lost, Mary M.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.55,1:46:40.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽說不是你的錯，但你輸了\N{\rENG}Ain't your fault, the way I heard it, but you lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.89,1:46:44.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能把你現在剩下的東西也輸掉\N{\rENG}Don't wanna lose the rest of what you got left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.06,1:46:46.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,對了\N{\rENG}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.93,1:46:57.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？\N{\rENG}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.17,1:46:59.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？\N{\rENG}Well, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.71,1:47:05.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽媽，你帶上瑪代爾和JD回家吧\N{\rENG}Mama, you take Mardell and J.D. And get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.98,1:47:10.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,別等我告訴律師 你擔心領不到社會福利...\N{\rENG}Before I tell that lawyer that you were so worried about your welfare...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.48,1:47:13.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,...所以根本就沒按規定 簽那些房產的證明\N{\rENG}...you never signed those house papers like you were supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.55,1:47:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以只要我願意 我可以把房子賣了...\N{\rENG}So any time I feel like it, I can sell that house...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.12,1:47:22.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,...不用理你這個又肥又懶的鄉巴佬\N{\rENG}...from under your fat, lazy, hillbilly asses.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.46,1:47:27.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你敢再來，我就那麼做\N{\rENG}And if you ever come back, that's exactly what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.04,1:48:13.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許應該有人數點到10\N{\rENG}Well, maybe someone ought to count to 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.72,1:48:28.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是很好聞吧，醫生？\N{\rENG}Don't smell real pretty, does it, doc?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.80,1:48:33.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,可能保不住了，麥琪\N{\rENG}We might have to lose it, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.37,1:49:53.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們拿掉了我的腿，老闆\N{\rENG}They took my leg, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.12,1:50:00.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會有事的，聽到嗎？\N{\rENG}It's gonna be all right, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.42,1:50:04.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我總能聽到你的聲音，老闆\N{\rENG}I always hear your voice, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.59,1:50:38.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,需要什麼嗎？\N{\rENG}You need anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.93,1:50:44.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想知道“莫 庫什勒”的意思\N{\rENG}I need to know what "mo cuishle" means.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.26,1:50:48.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,可是你沒有贏啊\N{\rENG}But you didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.67,1:50:50.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不用告訴你的\N{\rENG}I don't have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.30,1:50:56.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是我見過的最壞的人\N{\rENG}You're the meanest man I ever met.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.04,1:50:59.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,難怪沒有人愛你\N{\rENG}No wonder no one loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.91,1:51:05.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你讓我想起了我父親\N{\rENG}You remind me of my daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.02,1:51:09.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,他肯定是個...\N{\rENG}Well, he must have been...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.49,1:51:13.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,...非常聰明，英俊的人\N{\rENG}...a very intelligent, handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.63,1:51:20.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不會再讓我讀葉芝了，對吧？\N{\rENG}You ain't gonna make me talk no more Yeats, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.70,1:51:24.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，我...\N{\rENG}No, I was...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.64,1:51:28.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,...正在看城市大學的宣傳材料\N{\rENG}...Iooking at this catalog from City College.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.84,1:51:33.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想給你弄個輪椅...\N{\rENG}I thought I'd get you a wheelchair...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.61,1:51:37.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,...可以用吸管控制的那種\N{\rENG}...maybe the kind that operates by blowing through a straw.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.85,1:51:40.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你可能想去上學\N{\rENG}I thought maybe you'd like to go back to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.89,1:51:48.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,求你幫個忙，老闆\N{\rENG}I got a favor to ask you, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.53,1:51:52.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\rENG}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.63,1:51:55.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼事都行\N{\rENG}Anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.33,1:52:00.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,記得我爸是怎麼幫埃克斯的麼？\N{\rENG}Remember what my daddy did for Axel?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.18,1:52:15.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,想都不要想\N{\rENG}Don't even think about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.52,1:52:21.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能象現在這樣，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}I can't be like this, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.20,1:52:26.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,在我已經成就那麼多以後\N{\rENG}Not after what I done.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.13,1:52:29.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我見識了整個世界\N{\rENG}I seen the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.20,1:52:34.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,人們高呼我的名字\N{\rENG}People chanted my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.41,1:52:36.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,喔...\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.51,1:52:42.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,...不是我的本名 是你給我起的該死的名字\N{\rENG}...not my name, some damn name you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.02,1:52:47.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,可他們為我歡呼\N{\rENG}But they were chanting for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.02,1:52:53.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我上過雜志\N{\rENG}I was in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.16,1:52:59.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,你以為我以前做過這樣的夢麼？\N{\rENG}You think I ever dreamed that'd happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.33,1:53:08.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,我生出來的時候只有2磅1.5盎司\N{\rENG}I was born at 2 pounds, 1 and a half ounces.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.44,1:53:15.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸爸以前總說我是打拼 到這個世界上的...\N{\rENG}Daddy used to tell me I fought to get into this world...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.38,1:53:20.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,...我也會打出一片天地\N{\rENG}...and I'd fight my way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.69,1:53:28.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是我唯一想做的，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}That's all I wanna do, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.79,1:53:33.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是不想為那個和你打\N{\rENG}I just don't wanna fight you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.20,1:53:37.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我得到了我要的\N{\rENG}I got what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.57,1:53:44.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,全部都得到了\N{\rENG}I got it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.58,1:53:50.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,別讓他們從我身邊一點點地拿走\N{\rENG}Don't let them keep taking it away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.72,1:54:00.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,別讓我一直躺在這 直到聽不見人們的歡呼聲為止\N{\rENG}Don't let me lie here till I can't hear those people chanting no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.66,1:54:07.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\rENG}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.63,1:54:10.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\rENG}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.77,1:54:15.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜託，不要求我\N{\rENG}Please, don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.37,1:54:19.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在求呢\N{\rENG}I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.05,1:54:24.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\rENG}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.83,1:55:10.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,喂？\N{\rENG}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.49,1:55:17.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,午夜時分...\N{\rENG}In the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.93,1:55:21.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,...麥琪自己找到了辦法\N{\rENG}...Maggie had found her own solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.49,1:55:24.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,她咬舌了\N{\rENG}She had bit her tongue.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.74,1:55:34.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,停下來，停下來\N{\rENG}Stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.04,1:55:40.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,看著我，看著我\N{\rENG}Look at me. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.95,1:55:58.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,差點失血過多而死 直到他們把她的傷口縫合\N{\rENG}Nearly bled to death before they stitched her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.15,1:56:02.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,在弗蘭基到來以前，她恢復了知覺 把縫上的傷口又撕開了\N{\rENG}She came around and ripped them out before Frankie even got there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.83,1:56:05.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們又把傷口縫起來\N{\rENG}They stitched her up again...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.18,1:56:08.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,墊起了舌頭 以免她再咬舌自盡\N{\rENG}...padded the tongue so she couldn't bite.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.73,1:56:29.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不能那麼做，你知道的\N{\rENG}You can't do it, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.92,1:56:33.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道，神父\N{\rENG}I do, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.85,1:56:35.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,可你不知道她有多遲鈍\N{\rENG}But you don't know how thick she is...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.99,1:56:38.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,訓練她有多難\N{\rENG}...how hard it was to train her.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.97,1:56:43.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,其他拳手你叫他們做什麼 他們就做什麼\N{\rENG}Other fighters would do exactly what you'd say to them...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.02,1:56:48.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,但她卻會問為什麼這樣，為什麼那樣 然後還是按自己的方式去做\N{\rENG}...and she'd ask, why this and why that, and then do it her own way anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.69,1:56:51.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,她能去爭奪冠軍，我....\N{\rENG}How she fought for the title, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.10,1:56:53.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是靠任何....\N{\rENG}It wasn't by anything...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.80,1:56:56.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是靠聽我的話\N{\rENG}Well, it wasn't by listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.88,1:57:08.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是她現在想死\N{\rENG}But now she wants to die...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.34,1:57:10.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,而我只想把她留在我身邊\N{\rENG}...and I just wanna keep her with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.92,1:57:19.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我向上帝起誓，神父\N{\rENG}And I swear to God, Father, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.62,1:57:22.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣做是犯罪\N{\rENG}It's committing a sin by doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.66,1:57:26.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓她活下去，實際上是在殺死她\N{\rENG}By keeping her alive, I'm killing her.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.50,1:57:29.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你明白我的意思麼？ 我怎麼才能克服呢？\N{\rENG}Do you know what I mean? How do I get around that?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.83,1:57:33.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不需要，你不要插手，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}You don't. You step aside, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.84,1:57:35.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,把她交托給上帝\N{\rENG}You leave her with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.44,1:57:40.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,她沒有求上帝幫忙 她求我幫忙\N{\rENG}She's not asking for God's help. She's asking for mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.18,1:57:44.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,23年了，我基本上每天 都能在彌撒上見到你，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}Frankie, I've seen you at Mass almost every day for 23 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.35,1:57:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,只有那些為了某些事 而不能原諒自己的人\N{\rENG}The only person comes to church that much...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.52,1:57:48.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,才會這麼頻繁地來教堂\N{\rENG}...is the kind who can't forgive himself for something.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.35,1:57:50.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,無論你身上背負著什麼罪\N{\rENG}Whatever sins you're carrying...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.22,1:57:53.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,都無法和這個相提並論\N{\rENG}...they're nothing compared to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.45,1:57:58.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,忘記上帝，天堂和地獄吧\N{\rENG}Forget about God or heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.39,1:58:01.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你那麼做，你會迷失的\N{\rENG}If you do this thing, you'll be lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.93,1:58:07.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,深深地迷失\N{\rENG}Somewhere so deep...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.01,1:58:11.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,深到再也找不回自我了\N{\rENG}...you'll never find yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.61,1:58:20.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我已經是了\N{\rENG}I think I did it already.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.94,1:58:45.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們一直給她鎮靜劑 好保證她不會再那麼做\N{\rENG}We're keeping her sedated so she won't try that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.47,1:59:53.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我今早去看了麥琪\N{\rENG}I went to see Maggie this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.88,1:59:56.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一定是去了其他地方\N{\rENG}You must have been somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.05,1:59:59.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.75,2:00:05.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在和一個我不認識的對手奮戰？\N{\rENG}You got a fight I don't know about?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.26,2:00:13.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,那不是你的錯\N{\rENG}It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.96,2:00:16.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我當時那麼說是錯誤的\N{\rENG}I was wrong to say that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.37,2:00:18.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說得真對\N{\rENG}You're damn right.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.70,2:00:21.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,我給你找到一個拳手\N{\rENG}I found you a fighter...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.20,2:00:24.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你讓她發揮出了最大的潛力\N{\rENG}...and you made her the best fighter she could be.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.34,2:00:28.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,我殺了她\N{\rENG}I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.95,2:00:30.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,別那麼說\N{\rENG}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.21,2:00:33.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥琪走進那扇門的時候 除了膽量什麼都沒有\N{\rENG}Maggie walked through that door with nothing but guts.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.92,2:00:37.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,根本沒有機會實現她的夢想\N{\rENG}No chance in the world of being what she needed to be.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.29,2:00:40.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,一年半以後，她在爭奪世界冠軍\N{\rENG}A year and a half later, she's fighting for the championship of the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.86,2:00:42.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,是你的功勞\N{\rENG}You did that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.33,2:00:46.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,每天都有人死去的，弗蘭基\N{\rENG}People die every day, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.03,2:00:48.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,拖地的時候，刷碗的時候\N{\rENG}Mopping floors, washing dishes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.23,2:00:51.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道他們最後一個念頭是什麼嗎？\N{\rENG}And you know what their last thought is?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.33,2:00:53.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,“我從沒有過機會”\N{\rENG}"I never got my shot."
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.30,2:00:56.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為有你，麥琪得到了屬於她的機會\N{\rENG}Because of you, Maggie got her shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.84,2:01:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果她今天就死去 你知道她最後一個念頭是什麼嗎？\N{\rENG}If she dies today, you know what her last thought will be?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.41,2:01:04.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,“我覺得我幹得不錯”\N{\rENG}"I think I did all right."
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.39,2:01:14.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會覺得心安理得的\N{\rENG}I know I could rest with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.63,2:01:18.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.26,2:01:21.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.14,2:01:33.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.12,2:02:13.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,我去沖杯咖啡\N{\rENG}I'm gonna get a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.68,2:02:15.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.11,2:02:43.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.92,2:02:50.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會拔掉你的呼吸器...\N{\rENG}I'm gonna disconnect your air machine...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.25,2:02:53.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,...然後你就會睡著\N{\rENG}...then you're gonna go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.23,2:03:00.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後我給你打一針，你就...\N{\rENG}Then I'll give you a shot, and you'II...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.06,2:03:03.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,...會一直睡下去\N{\rENG}...stay asleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.01,2:03:10.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,“莫 庫什勒”...\N{\rENG}Mo cuishle...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.34,2:03:15.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,...的意思是“我的摯愛，我的血肉”\N{\rENG}...means "my darling, my blood."
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.01,2:04:26.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,他只給她打了一針\N{\rENG}He gave her a single shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.18,2:04:31.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,腎上腺素的劑量是需要量的好幾倍\N{\rENG}It was enough adrenaline to do the job a few times over.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.75,2:04:34.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,他不想讓她再受一次苦\N{\rENG}He didn't want her going through this again.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.47,2:05:26.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後他走出門去\N{\rENG}Then he walked out.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.78,2:05:30.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想他什麼都沒有了\N{\rENG}I don't think he had anything left.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.63,2:05:50.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我回到拳擊館\N{\rENG}I went back to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.17,2:05:54.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,等待著，認為他總有一天會回來\N{\rENG}Waited, figuring he'd turn up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.46,2:06:17.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,就在那時一個鬼魂走進門來\N{\rENG}And that's when a ghost came through the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.43,2:06:23.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想過你說的話了 斯科雷普先生\N{\rENG}I got to thinking what you said, Mr.Scrap.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.57,2:06:26.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,結果呢，丹吉爾？\N{\rENG}What was that, Danger?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.84,2:06:30.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個人都會失敗的\N{\rENG}Anybody can lose one fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.67,2:06:33.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是實話\N{\rENG}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.34,2:06:36.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,去吧，戴上手套 你已經很長時間沒訓練了\N{\rENG}Go on, put your gloves on. You missed a lot of training.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.88,2:06:41.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的，斯科雷普先生，沒問題\N{\rENG}Will do, Mr.Scrap. Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.17,2:07:04.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基再也沒回來\N{\rENG}Frankie never came back at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.91,2:07:08.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,（兇狠是不夠的）
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.09,2:07:22.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗蘭基沒留下訊息 沒人知道他去了哪\N{\rENG}Frankie didn't leave a note, and nobody knew where he went.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.59,2:07:25.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,我希望他是去找你了\N{\rENG}I'd hoped he'd gone to find you...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.29,2:07:28.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,去再次請求你的原諒\N{\rENG}...and ask you one more time to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.46,2:07:32.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,但也許他心中什麼都沒有了\N{\rENG}But maybe he didn't have anything left in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.07,2:07:35.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只希望他能找到個地方 享受片刻的安寧\N{\rENG}I just hope he found someplace where he could find a little peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.94,2:07:39.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個雪松和橡樹環繞\N{\rENG}A place set in the cedars and oak trees.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.38,2:07:42.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,比偏僻更偏僻的地方\N{\rENG}Somewhere between nowhere and goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.75,2:07:46.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,但那可能只是一廂情願\N{\rENG}But that's probably wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.82,2:07:49.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,無論他在哪兒\N{\rENG}No matter where he is...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.35,2:07:55.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你該知道你父親 究竟是個什麼樣的人\N{\rENG}...I thought you should know what kind of man your father really was.
